Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入自動激光模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,606 808回收完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 航向0300 第二戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
