Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光瞄準前方 準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被浪擋過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯戈 主炮發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號2號炮塔能量充填
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射角修正 偏左3.6
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那可惡的臭科拉利安害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是我的技術變差了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下 這樣下去要相撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想撞過去麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打近身戰的話 科拉利安就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難影響到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在交錯的時候 把全部彈藥一起打過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和他們同歸於盡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也有同樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你死我活的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開所有導彈發射管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有導彈準備發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離200 150 100 50
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 那是…誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右翼 VRF脫落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力降低25％
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔爾荷 調整左右的光粒子平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:15:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才好像有人叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰 色狼 流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我沒那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在和什麼人做什麼 安妮莫奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們不打算離開這片空域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉著圈飛的話 遲早會再次碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候就要分勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 肯戈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這次一定不會打偏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 知道麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上毫無來由的惡意多不勝數哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不理解 你也不可能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那的確存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 這裡那裡到處都是 毫無名目的惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤爾根斯艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於由我作為負責人進行指揮一事您有所不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加之過去的原因 我能夠理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種小事你還在意麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太被人小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在為了保護安妮莫奈和終式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您聽我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請趁光粒子的濃度變稀的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收終式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然中了彈 但月光號的行動還不明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能隨便移動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 明明是你叫了我我才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我叫的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 不是我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 像你這種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現月光號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能飛麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定解決你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 這種距離怎麼可能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 不愧是肯戈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭頓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優萊卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片空域的光粒子正迅速消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在科拉利安的消失地點邂逅的少年們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不清楚其中意義的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為了彼此所要守護的人而奮鬥著
